Type: Package
Package: llm
Title: LLM Usage Tracking and Visualization Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: John Gavin
Maintainer: John Gavin <john.gavin@example.com>
Description: Tools for tracking and visualizing LLM usage including cost tracking,
    token monitoring, progress bars, and Max5 5-hour block usage displays.
    Provides functions for analyzing Claude Code usage patterns.
